org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT gpx_files.id AS alias_0, gpx_files.id FROM gpx_files INNER JOIN gpx_file_tags ON gpx_file_tags.gpx_id = gpx_files.id LEFT OUTER JOIN users ON users.id = gpx_files.user_id WHERE gpx_files.visible = "$1" AND (visibility IN ('public', 'identifiable') OR user_id = 2236) AND gpx_file_tags.tag = "$2" AND gpx_files.visible = "$3" ORDER BY gpx_files.id DESC LIMIT "$4" OFFSET "$5"
